<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٨٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذِي الْقَرْنَيْنِ}</span> ... مَلِكٍ صَالِحٍ عَادِلٍ مَلَكَ مَا بَيْنَ المَشْرِقِ وَالمَغْرِبِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٨٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبَبًا}</span> ... أَسْبَابًا وَطُرُقًا تُوَصِّلُهُ إِلَى مَا يُرِيدُ مِنْ فَتْحِ الُمدُنِ، وَقَهْرِ الأَعْدَاءِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٨٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَتْبَعَ سَبَبًا}</span> ... أَخَذَ جَادًّا بِالأَسْبَابِ وَالطُّرُقِ المُوصِلَةِ إِلَى مَا يُريدُ بِجِدٍّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٨٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَجَدَهَا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> وَجَدَهَا كَذَلِكَ فِي نَظَرِ العَيْنِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٨٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَمِئَةٍ}</span> ... حَارَّةٍ ذَاتِ طِينٍ أَسْوَدَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٨٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُّكْرًا}</span> ... عَظِيمًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
