<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خُبْرًا}</span> ... عِلْمًا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٩٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السَّدَّيْنِ}</span> ... الجَبَلَيْنِ الحَاجِزَيْنِ لِمَا وَرَاءَهُمَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٩٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَاجُوجَ وَمَاجُوجَ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هُمَا:</span> أُمَّتَانِ عَظِيمَتَانِ كَثِيرَتَا العَدَدِ مِنْ بَنِي آدَمَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
